frontmatter.title: Common Questions
frontmatter.meta_title: MStore Shop - Universal mobile commerce app by React native for Shopify store
frontmatter.meta_description: You are shop-owners of physical stores with high-traffic consumers and think to go digital. Or you are online shop-owners with Shopify store/website. Both of you want to maximize sale opportunities.

markdownRemark.html:
If you have issue when installing, please post one ticket to the Github. Also provide the purchase screenshot and your username on codecanyon. Our technical team will help to check and feedback.

https://github.com/inspireui/support/issues
